I added the door with metal mesh to give it some extra texture and to put away things that wouldn’t look stylish if they were exposed. 

3. Try to use natural wood. The bookshelves before were white compressed wood. I generally try to use natural wood as you can always catch the natural texture it has. When it comes to color, my favorite is always white oak.
